headline: Jim Cramer on AT&T: “This Thing is a Really Good Situation”
summary: AT&T Inc. (NYSE:T) is one of the stocks that Jim Cramer shed light on. A caller asked for Cramer’s opinion on the company. In response, he said: “Now remember, I infamously didn’t like it at 22. So you could say, what are you doing liking it at 28? But I did change my mind at […]
